videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield gets the steal and sends a nice pass to Katie Lou Samuelson who makes the layup.
videos.headline: UConn turns steal into Samuelson layup

videos.description: Jessica Shepard backs down her defender, spins and makes the shot plus the foul.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Shepard spins and makes and-1 layup

videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield drives and makes a nice pass to Azura Stevens who makes the layup.
videos.headline: UConn steal leads to Stevens layup

videos.description: Kia Nurse two consecutive baskets help complete Connecticut's comeback victory over Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Nurse's two straight baskets seal victory for UConn

videos.description: Five Connecticut players score in double figures as the top-ranked Huskies improve to 7-0 with an 80-71 win over No. 3 Notre Dame.
videos.headline: UConn rallies past Notre Dame to remain undefeated
